seo: 万户OA,任意文件下载漏洞,download_ftp.jsp,漏洞检测
seo_en: Wanhu OA, Arbitrary File Download Vulnerability, download_ftp.jsp, Vulnerability Detection
summary: 该插件用于检测万户OA系统中download_ftp.jsp文件存在的任意文件下载漏洞，攻击者可能利用此漏洞下载服务器上的任意文件
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the arbitrary file download vulnerability in the download_ftp.jsp file of Wanhu OA system. Attackers may exploit this vulnerability to download any file from the server
